snippet.title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (PS2/Xbox/GC/GBA/PC) (2004) Video Game UK Teaser
snippet.description:
UK Teaser for the Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban video game, based on the book and the 2004 movie of the same name.

Platforms this game was released: PlayStation 2, Xbox, Nintendo GameCube, Windows, Game Boy Advance
